{"tid":306570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(jj插沙)我好想搵返呢隻錢罌","createTime":"2017-07-02T15:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T14:37:11.000Z","uid":97958,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a82bb0b49f8585464faa6ec37924bd3215fc1a67","tid":306570,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 事源係一個由細到大好錫我既堂家姐突然過左身，我好掛住佢，我知人死不能復生，但我都想拎返我細個送俾佢陪左佢好多年既錢罌，得閒睇下懷念下以前同佢玩既日子，但我去佢間房發現已經唔見左⋯<br />\n<br />\n因為唔想提起佢屋企人既傷心事，所以唔敢問佢屋企人<br />\n<br />\n我想買返個一模一樣既錢罌睇下都好，但可惜既係個錢罌係小學既時候老師送既而我亦冇影低相，根本搵唔到邊到有，所以想麻煩各位巴絲打幫幫手睇下會唔會係邊度見過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/234148_4674f8f110d0cf46cf7e6e6e769f96fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F234148_4674f8f110d0cf46cf7e6e6e769f96fc.jpg&h=a5f30de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我知自己畫得唔好，但我已經盡左力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個錢罌係士多啤梨形狀既，印象中係有3隻熊仔，士多啤梨係一間雪糕鋪，有一隻熊仔係入面遞緊一杯好似係白色既雪糕俾出面既熊，另外好似仲有隻熊企左係另一邊同埋士多啤梨外面有盞路燈<br />\n<br />\nSorry講到1999咁，唔該各位巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8397cfb33da042d54fedca95804fd0dcf5fd3c","tid":306570,"uid":97958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:53:47.000Z","msg":"補充返我記得另外仲有款係菠蘿既"},{"pid":"ccdfad18985215523ca8025ccf67c5b7cad67523","tid":306570,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推下"},{"pid":"6078b246333b0e561e733fa0e36839b3cc0d63c6","tid":306570,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:10:40.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n但應該好難"},{"pid":"6cedfdead07067028a927224e950b9fdb6f1bbf9","tid":306570,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T23:31:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推<br />\n但應該好難</blockquote><br />\n唔該，我都知好難，但都想問下睇下有冇人見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceae5750414b8c58e565d98d42ae6b369316bbc1","tid":306570,"uid":85964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T23:45:21.000Z","msg":"可以去陶瓷班自己整"},{"pid":"fdcf0fc87e923c982788b5fbce34835cb5b0317e","tid":306570,"uid":36780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T23:56:50.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"17c6a596b35a56b8d3d2ddc20374945fb802d85e","tid":306570,"uid":43372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T23:58:18.000Z","msg":"未見過幫推"},{"pid":"fb0aecd8f050b1a8b0b335b4be0fc7ec6194a122","tid":306570,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以去陶瓷班自己整</blockquote><br />\n但因為佢個形都幾難，我諗唔係初學者會整到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3787168e5a8337b5184f3b8df2006675e3bef5ae","tid":306570,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:44:18.000Z","msg":"去舊果啲文具店唔知有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d0f71ec0d6ca4c99835a1b1108b49ed8e984b2","tid":306570,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:48:59.000Z","msg":"未見過， 幫推"},{"pid":"de2b9e479700a155e4b04037a3fca03464e2fa19","tid":306570,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed440f79065a45bcfdd991fea2449ec0af15dc07","tid":306570,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:39:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去舊果啲文具店唔知有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下去睇先，因為嗰個錢罌都好似成十幾年前⋯<br />\n我都閒要搵返一樣既好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7ed17e4b2c324f638d4fd023ac3047b53025f6","tid":306570,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去舊果啲文具店唔知有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下去睇先，因為嗰個錢罌都好似成十幾年前⋯<br />\n我都<span style=\"color: red;\">明</span>要搵返一樣既好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"34cb5b882a6677d98b00abf9f22eaabdfc7a8b27","tid":306570,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T14:37:11.000Z","msg":"推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}